Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the report said...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire village is devastated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet there's not a drop of blood,\Nlet alone any bodies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... the villagers of Ragako\Nwere able to safely evacuate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the Titans were having\Na field day in a completely empty village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore... why would they evacuate\Nwithout even taking a single horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moblit, I found one! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moblit, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a portrait of \NConny Springer's parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strong possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Children"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be your petty life...\Nor Christa's future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something! Who's the enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scouts... are already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiner. What are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, I'm a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying to trust Ymir as a warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the one who ate Marcel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's my point. \NYmir's motive is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she turned human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she probably roamed around\Nand lived only caring about herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until she met Christa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as cute as Christa is, we have\Nother reasons to bring her to our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an important person\Nin a family of the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Eren turns out not to be the Coordinate,\Nour job isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having Christa with us at that point\Nwill make our search much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they planning to leave \Nbefore the sun sets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can take Annie, Christa, \Nand that back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way we won't have to come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. And our mission will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get to our hometown,\Ntell Annie how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stare too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough that everyone can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both murderers with short lives ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who better to understand what\Nwe've gone through than one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Reiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we waiting until night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. We're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren, don't try to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't get violent with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the shape that I'm in.\NDoes it look like I can resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll slaughter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll kill you!\N--Hey. Why are we leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let go!\N--Ymir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you turned back into a human,\Ndo you remember the person you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it was five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it one of your comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for not even remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault for forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same for us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren doesn't seem to remember either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you resent me for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure... I... don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably didn't want\Nto eat a human either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were you wandering\Noutside the walls for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like... I was stuck in\Na nightmare that would never  end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red smoke signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way around!\NShould we head towards it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Any detours and we'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll force our way through!\NAll soldiers, prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's get to a place without Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get as far away as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Titan form isn't very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get surrounded,\NI won't be able to protect you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't we just \Nwait until nightfall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke signals?\NDid the Scouts come to rescue us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless they brought loads \Nof horses over the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that scouting formation won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone made that call...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would happen so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Commander Erwin.\NA tough opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... They're already that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Eren's fault for going berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiner! Christa's here!\NChrista came with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want her, now's the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know? You can't see her from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a good-natured \Nperson, it's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee she came to save me! I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's true, it's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our chance of succeeding is way too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you get Christa \Nout of that formation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Will that be after\NI'm eaten by one of your warriors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me! Christa is \Nindispensable to us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get her now!\NGo prove it to me this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...\NI'll never get a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:56.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Information Available for Public Disclosure"\N"Ymir's Hometown"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:56.07,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"It is not known where Ymir's hometown is located.\N However, its location is most certainly\N outside the confines of the walls."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Ymir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know if we can escape \Nourselves, let alone go back for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone, it's Christa I want\Nto save from this conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust us! So just bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for Christa's \Nown sake! Got it, Ymir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... really for Christa's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening again, Christa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and yet it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I have to lie to myself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Here's a promising one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there. You're going to\Ncome live with us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to live a brand-new life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brand-new life... needs a brand-new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day... was the first \Ntime I lied to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that point on, I convinced myself...\Nthat I never had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is this Lady Ymir who inherits\Nthe blood of the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Lady Ymir is with us,\Nwe will be blessed with immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... it wasn't all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My food wasn't cold anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And neither was my bed off the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Ymir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more than all... was the feeling\Nof being needed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I served a purpose in someone's life\Nfor the first time ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that was more precious\Nthan anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her! She's the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told us she has the blood of the king!\NAll we did was believe her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was cruelly reminded\Nthat everything in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:13:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ymir! The blood of the king\Nruns through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once again... I told more lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it took \Nto save everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things didn't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Please, stop! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I was being punished\Nfor deceiving all those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for convincing myself to believe...\Nto feel needed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I deserved for\Ncontinuing to lie to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Titan! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what I saw was freedom \Nspread out before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was such a thing as fate,\NI can only laugh at how fickle it can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I made a promise to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was done with telling lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to lie to myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From then on, I'd live honest to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What ever happened with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was given the name Christa Lenz\Nand sent off to become a cadet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity. She would have been\Nbetter off not being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. It makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're trying to do something "nice," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell right away...\N...that you were the same as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you fed yourself lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were someone desperately trying\Nto convince yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Christa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I won't ask you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you give me one last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be honest with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this environment, I'm \Nthe strongest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Quit it, Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think a forest like this\Nis where I can shine the most? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir! Stop! We'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I became a Titan, I might be\Npowerless compared to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can jump through the \Ntrees and move swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could snatch Eren away from you\Nand go back to meet up with the Scouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and probably succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't agree to take\NChrista with you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get in your way and \Nfight you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!\NDon't you care what happens to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help her that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means taking her future away,\NI'll do what it takes to live and meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be the shittiest \Nperson there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't know what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows how awful I am,\Nand yet she still smiles at me... that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay and fight, it should be easier\Nfor you to escape anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you rather stay \Nand kill each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to prove how crazy I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead in the forest! I saw a light!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the light that appears\Nwhen a Titan transforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers, disperse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe the enemy has already transformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locate Eren and recover him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of the Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle is not our objective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prioritize recovery and retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phil! Round up the horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing is to find the enemy\Nand let the others know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be fleeing from the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the scream of a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one they took! In Titan form!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ymir! Why are you the only one here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Eren?!\NWhat about Reiner!? Bertholdt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Ymir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she turn into a Titan\Nand fight with Reiner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get away from Reiner?!\NWhere are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us anything, Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ugly! We're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she keeping an eye out for Reiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... is she looking \Nat everybody one by one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ymir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate Christa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there! Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast! We're losing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Ymir do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the only one who could've \Nguessed it would turn out this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She's clearly hostile to us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's cooperating with Reiner!\NShe lured us right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes, Reiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eren's being taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your horse and chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting him back no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means trading my life for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle of pursuit begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hunters and the hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intense emotions of friends made foe...\Nspill and clash on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But soldiers are falling far too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a gamble waging the fate of humanity,\NErwin executes a do-or-die strategy.
